titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on N,N-dimethyl-N'-(3-((methylamino)carbonyl)oxy)phenyl)methanimidamide monohydrochloride.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S2429)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 3/4/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1994, the duty on n,n-dimethyl-n'(3-((methylamino)-carbonyl)oxy)-phenyl)-methanimidamide monohydrochloride.
